Titolo: Earthlock

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Earthlock (formerly titled Earthlock: Festival of Magic) is a role-playing video game developed and published by the Norwegian company Snowcastle Games for Microsoft Windows, OS X, Linux, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and Wii U. The Xbox One version was launched on September 1, 2016 worldwide.The PC/Mac version, initially planned for release at the same time as the Xbox One release, was postponed to September 27, 2016. The game is planned to be the first volume of an Earthlock trilogy. A version for the Nintendo Switch was released on March 8, 2018.
A sequel, titled Earthlock 2, is scheduled for a 2022 release.